Question:Find the number is positive or negative
Example:Input:1 output:positive
Step1:Understand the problem
what is given?number 1
What is required?check + or -
step2:Manual thinking
1-->1>0-->positive else 1<0-->negative
step3:Break into small steps
1.Take a i/p
2.check the i/p is greater than zero means print positive
3.check the i/p is less than zero means print negative
step4:write logic in english
1.I will take i/p
2.use if i/p is greater than zero print positive
3.else print negative
step5:convert logic into python code
number=10
if number>0: 
   print("positive")
else:
  print("negative")
